<div><head>Vers 46</head><!--Luc 20, 46-->
    
    <p xml:id=""><!-- interlinearis-->
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/lc20_46" synch="1-3"><lb ed="#S"/>Attendite a scribis</quote>
            <p><!-- marginalis--><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/lc20_46" synch="1-3"><lb ed="#S"/>ATTENDITE A  SCRIBIS.</quote> Duplici ratione iubemur attendere a vane 
                <lb ed="#S"/>glorie cupidis, ne vel eorum simulatione decipiamur, vel eorum exemplo ad 
                <lb ed="#S"/>amorem temporalium inflamemur.</p>
        </p>
        <p><!-- interlinearis--><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/lc20_46" synch="4-8">qui 
            <lb ed="#S"/>volunt ambulare in stolis</quote>
            <p><!-- interlinearis--><lb ed="#S"/>culcioribus vestimen
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>tis induti in publicum procedere quod reprehendi
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>tur in divite qui induebatur purpura et bisso</p>
        </p>
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/lc20_46" synch="9-23">et amant 
            <lb ed="#S"/>salutationes in foro et primas ca¬
            <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>thedras in synagogis et primos 
            <lb ed="#S"/>discubitus in conviviis.</quote>
            <p><!-- marginalis--><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/lc20_46" synch="9-13"><lb ed="#S"/>ET AMANT  SALUTA
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>TIONES  IN  FORO.</quote> Non 
                <lb ed="#S"/>salutari in foro, nec pri
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>mas sedes vetat eis qui¬
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>bus debetur ex ordine of
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>ficii, sed eis qui inde¬
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>bite amant. Animum 
                <lb ed="#S"/>enim non gradum redar
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>guit. Nec vero caret 
                <lb ed="#S"/>culpa, si is fori litibus in
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>teresse velit qui deside
                <lb ed="#S"/>rat sedere in cathedra 
                <lb ed="#S"/>moysi.</p>
        </p>
    </p>
</div>
